            <string name="rivanced_gms_core_dialog_not_whitelisted_not_allowed_in_background_message">"I-MicroG GmsCore ayinayo imvume yokusebenza ngemuva.\n\nLandela umhlahlandlela othi \"Ungabulali uhlelo lwami lokusebenza\" wefoni yakho, bese usebenzisa imiyalelo ekufakweni kwe-MicroG yakho.\n\nLokhu kuyadingeka ukuze uhlelo lokusebenza lusebenze."</string>
