            <string name="rivanced_gms_core_dialog_not_whitelisted_using_battery_optimizations_message">"Ukwenziwa kahle kwebhethri ye-MicroG GmsCore kufanele kukhutshazwe ukuze kuvinjelwe izinkinga.\n\nUkukhubaza ukwenziwa kahle kwebhethri kwe-MicroG ngeke kuthinte kabi ukusetshenziswa kwebhethri.\n\nThepha inkinobho ethi qhubeka bese uvumela izinguquko zokwenziwa kahle."</string>
